{"tid":1962433,"cid":10,"subCid":0,"title":"疫情影響日本供貨   任天堂 Switch 主機本周將不會出貨","createTime":"2020-04-07T12:55:22.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-08T03:53:07.000Z","uid":28114,"like":4,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"e4af552a3bd0d8c0a58373b6cac98f7a2cc6d6d8","tid":1962433,"uid":28114,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-07T12:55:22.000Z","msg":"日本任天堂今日（7 日）透過官方 Twitter 宣佈，除事前預約者外， Switch 主機本體（包括《集合啦！動物森友會》特別版主機）以及 Switch Lite 均不會在本周出貨，而下週以後的出貨預定計畫將在稍後日除再作公佈。<br />\n<br />\n任天堂在上星期曾表示，受武漢肺炎疫情影響，在中國工廠生產的 Switch 主機及 Joy-Con 等設備的製造及運輸都有所延遲， 受到影響的不僅是日本，美國和歐洲也在努力跟上需求，惟情況暫時並未有改善。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://unwire.hk/2020/04/07/switch-demand/game-channel/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Funwire.hk%2F2020%2F04%2F07%2Fswitch-demand%2Fgame-channel%2F&d=BHyrWEjohbhGCquuSPOYYp1e7EkIXHZyG33jvsgDPMQ%3D&h=d560a34f\" target=\"_blank\">https://unwire.hk/2020/04/07/switch-demand/game-channel/</a>"},{"pid":"c2992526614f9d3f492a99aea39b2f381c61945e","tid":1962433,"uid":94828,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-07T13:14:02.000Z","msg":"連登仔：電子垃圾冇人買"},{"pid":"78752637301c21718c80f59dc2d73933ef4aacb7","tid":1962433,"uid":312692,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-07T15:48:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />日日都有大貨番"},{"pid":"7e1aa405fdad5cea8f397b56743a14d708e813d8","tid":1962433,"uid":28114,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-08T03:53:07.000Z","msg":"日本任天堂宣佈本週以後，Switch 主機供貨無期<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://chinese.engadget.com/chinese-2020-04-07-nintendo-switch-supply-unstable-ncov-19.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fchinese.engadget.com%2Fchinese-2020-04-07-nintendo-switch-supply-unstable-ncov-19.html&d=BHyrWEjohbhGCquuSPOYYp1e7EkIXHZyG33jvsgDPMQ%3D&h=43579ce9\" target=\"_blank\">https://chinese.engadget.com/chinese-2020-04-07-nintendo-switch-supply-unstable-ncov-19.